<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْبَيِّنَةُ}</span> ... العَلَامَةُ الَّتِي وُعِدُوا بِهَا فِي الكُتُبِ السَّابِقَةِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَسُولٌ مِّنَ اللَّهِ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> وَالبَيِّنَةُ رَسُولٌ مِنَ اللهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
